OL,3,CTwo escape injury following arson
OL,4,Cattack in Downpatrick
OL,6,FTwo people have escaped injury
OL,7,Ffollowing an arson attack at a house
OL,8,Fin Co Down.
OL,10,FDetectives are appealing for
OL,11,Finformation about the incident at
OL,12,Faround 1.50am on Saturday at the
OL,13,Fproperty in the Saul Street area of
OL,14,FDownpatrick.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
