OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774725063
OL,3,CTwo escape injury following arson
OL,4,Cattack in Downpatrick
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesman said officers, as
OL,7,Fwell as colleagues from the Northern
OL,8,FIreland Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,9,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance
OL,10,FService, attended the scene, where the
OL,11,Ffront door of a house was on fire and
OL,12,Fa number of ground-floor windows were
OL,13,Fsmashed.
OL,15,FThey added: "However, the two people
OL,16,Fwho were in the property at the time
OL,17,Fof the attack were able to exit the
OL,18,Fhouse safely and no injuries were
OL,19,Freported.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
