OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774725063
OL,3,CTwo escape injury following arson
OL,4,Cattack in Downpatrick
OL,6,F"This was obviously a shock for them,
OL,7,Fhowever, and there was significant
OL,8,Fdamage caused to their home."
OL,10,FPolice said the incident is being
OL,11,Ftreated as deliberate ignition and as
OL,12,Farson with intent to endanger life.
OL,14,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,15,Fcome forward.
